{"tid":1681784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］慈善戰線第二波 打爆奶共show （咪撚睇CCTV）","createTime":"2019-10-29T15:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:56:13.000Z","uid":244122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b93eac4606decf0743dadc1264b38ae8a26835d6","tid":1681784,"uid":244122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"之前有手足開post 屌爆啲社福機構，話佢地收左194億又唔做嘢：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1679660/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1679660/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n咁岩比我發現仁愛堂今個星期六係Cc tvb 開show<br />\n我即刻就上網查下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仁愛堂</span></span>啦，點知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zezhfxT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzezhfxT.png&h=61234a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喂，唔係唔做野呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvPQ6C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvPQ6C.png&h=552c7827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建立黃色生活圈</span></span>"},{"pid":"075099226826f39625814f847eb1c39e8548664d","tid":1681784,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人(眾籌到而家先30%, 仲要大家支持) <br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg8yZng7